{
  "video_id": "apbSsILLh28",
  "title": "What really matters at the end of life | BJ Miller",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13999.0,
      "end_time": 18898.0,
      "text": "Well, we all need a reason to wake up."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18898.0,
      "end_time": 23068.0,
      "text": "For me, it just took 11,000 volts."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23068.0,
      "end_time": 24766.0,
      "text": "I know you're too polite to ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24766.0,
      "end_time": 27354.0,
      "text": "so I will tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27354.0,
      "end_time": 29601.0,
      "text": "One night, sophomore year of college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29601.0,
      "end_time": 33323.0,
      "text": "just back from Thanksgiving holiday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33323.0,
      "end_time": 35999.0,
      "text": "a few of my friends and I were horsing around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35999.0,
      "end_time": 40167.0,
      "text": "and we decided to climb atop a parked commuter train."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40167.0,
      "end_time": 43305.0,
      "text": "It was just sitting there, with the wires that run overhead."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43305.0,
      "end_time": 46804.0,
      "text": "Somehow, that seemed like a great idea at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46804.0,
      "end_time": 50270.0,
      "text": "We'd certainly done stupider things."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50270.0,
      "end_time": 53315.0,
      "text": "I scurried up the ladder on the back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53315.0,
      "end_time": 55061.0,
      "text": "and when I stood up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55061.0,
      "end_time": 58667.0,
      "text": "the electrical current entered my arm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58667.0,
      "end_time": 63699.0,
      "text": "blew down and out my feet, and that was that."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63699.0,
      "end_time": 68216.0,
      "text": "Would you believe that watch still works?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68216.0,
      "end_time": 69447.0,
      "text": "Takes a licking!"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69447.0,
      "end_time": 70502.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70502.0,
      "end_time": 75295.0,
      "text": "My father wears it now in solidarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75295.0,
      "end_time": 81342.0,
      "text": "That night began my formal relationship with death -- my death --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81342.0,
      "end_time": 85174.0,
      "text": "and it also began my long run as a patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85174.0,
      "end_time": 86352.0,
      "text": "It's a good word."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86352.0,
      "end_time": 88825.0,
      "text": "It means one who suffers."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88825.0,
      "end_time": 91607.0,
      "text": "So I guess we're all patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91607.0,
      "end_time": 93997.0,
      "text": "Now, the American health care system"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93997.0,
      "end_time": 97142.0,
      "text": "has more than its fair share of dysfunction --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97142.0,
      "end_time": 99750.0,
      "text": "to match its brilliance, to be sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99750.0,
      "end_time": 104226.0,
      "text": "I'm a physician now, a hospice and palliative medicine doc,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104226.0,
      "end_time": 107076.0,
      "text": "so I've seen care from both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107076.0,
      "end_time": 110999.0,
      "text": "And believe me: almost everyone who goes into healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110999.0,
      "end_time": 114874.0,
      "text": "really means well -- I mean, truly."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114874.0,
      "end_time": 118831.0,
      "text": "But we who work in it are also unwitting agents"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118831.0,
      "end_time": 123999.0,
      "text": "for a system that too often does not serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123999.0,
      "end_time": 125624.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125624.0,
      "end_time": 129029.0,
      "text": "Well, there's actually a pretty easy answer to that question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129029.0,
      "end_time": 131301.0,
      "text": "and it explains a lot:"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131301.0,
      "end_time": 138419.0,
      "text": "because healthcare was designed with diseases, not people, at its center."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138419.0,
      "end_time": 142158.0,
      "text": "Which is to say, of course, it was badly designed."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 142158.0,
      "end_time": 148234.0,
      "text": "And nowhere are the effects of bad design more heartbreaking"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 148234.0,
      "end_time": 151593.0,
      "text": "or the opportunity for good design more compelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 151593.0,
      "end_time": 153758.0,
      "text": "than at the end of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153758.0,
      "end_time": 158234.0,
      "text": "where things are so distilled and concentrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 158234.0,
      "end_time": 162073.0,
      "text": "There are no do-overs."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162073.0,
      "end_time": 166588.0,
      "text": "My purpose today is to reach out across disciplines"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166588.0,
      "end_time": 171495.0,
      "text": "and invite design thinking into this big conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 171495.0,
      "end_time": 176876.0,
      "text": "That is, to bring intention and creativity"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 176876.0,
      "end_time": 181235.0,
      "text": "to the experience of dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 181235.0,
      "end_time": 185292.0,
      "text": "We have a monumental opportunity in front of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185292.0,
      "end_time": 189657.0,
      "text": "before one of the few universal issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 189657.0,
      "end_time": 192991.0,
      "text": "as individuals as well as a civil society:"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 192991.0,
      "end_time": 199489.0,
      "text": "to rethink and redesign how it is we die."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 199489.0,
      "end_time": 203611.0,
      "text": "So let's begin at the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 203611.0,
      "end_time": 207570.0,
      "text": "For most people, the scariest thing about death isn't being dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 207570.0,
      "end_time": 209809.0,
      "text": "it's dying, suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 209809.0,
      "end_time": 212461.0,
      "text": "It's a key distinction."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 212461.0,
      "end_time": 214653.0,
      "text": "To get underneath this, it can be very helpful"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 214653.0,
      "end_time": 219031.0,
      "text": "to tease out suffering which is necessary as it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 219031.0,
      "end_time": 222317.0,
      "text": "from suffering we can change."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 222317.0,
      "end_time": 227577.0,
      "text": "The former is a natural, essential part of life, part of the deal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 227577.0,
      "end_time": 235013.0,
      "text": "and to this we are called to make space, adjust, grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 235013.0,
      "end_time": 241098.0,
      "text": "It can be really good to realize forces larger than ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 241098.0,
      "end_time": 244246.0,
      "text": "They bring proportionality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 244246.0,
      "end_time": 248779.0,
      "text": "like a cosmic right-sizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 248779.0,
      "end_time": 251237.0,
      "text": "After my limbs were gone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 251237.0,
      "end_time": 255847.0,
      "text": "that loss, for example, became fact, fixed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 255847.0,
      "end_time": 259184.0,
      "text": "necessarily part of my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 259184.00000000003,
      "end_time": 267173.0,
      "text": "and I learned that I could no more reject this fact than reject myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 267173.0,
      "end_time": 270572.0,
      "text": "It took me a while, but I learned it eventually."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 270572.0,
      "end_time": 273040.0,
      "text": "Now, another great thing about necessary suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 273040.0,
      "end_time": 276572.0,
      "text": "is that it is the very thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 276572.0,
      "end_time": 281999.0,
      "text": "that unites caregiver and care receiver --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 281999.0,
      "end_time": 285089.0,
      "text": "human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 285089.0,
      "end_time": 289673.0,
      "text": "This, we are finally realizing, is where healing happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 289673.0,
      "end_time": 293217.0,
      "text": "Yes, compassion -- literally, as we learned yesterday --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 293217.0,
      "end_time": 296672.0,
      "text": "suffering together."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 296672.0,
      "end_time": 300034.0,
      "text": "Now, on the systems side, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 300034.0,
      "end_time": 304376.0,
      "text": "so much of the suffering is unnecessary, invented."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 304376.0,
      "end_time": 306674.0,
      "text": "It serves no good purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 306674.0,
      "end_time": 310999.0,
      "text": "But the good news is, since this brand of suffering is made up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 310999.0,
      "end_time": 313681.0,
      "text": "well, we can change it."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 313681.0,
      "end_time": 318446.0,
      "text": "How we die is indeed something we can affect."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 318446.0,
      "end_time": 322523.0,
      "text": "Making the system sensitive to this fundamental distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 322523.0,
      "end_time": 325999.0,
      "text": "between necessary and unnecessary suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 325999.0,
      "end_time": 330299.0,
      "text": "gives us our first of three design cues for the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 330299.0,
      "end_time": 334852.0,
      "text": "After all, our role as caregivers, as people who care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 334852.0,
      "end_time": 342292.0,
      "text": "is to relieve suffering -- not add to the pile."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 342292.0,
      "end_time": 344187.0,
      "text": "True to the tenets of palliative care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 344187.0,
      "end_time": 347884.0,
      "text": "I function as something of a reflective advocate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 347884.0,
      "end_time": 351177.0,
      "text": "as much as prescribing physician."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 351177.0,
      "end_time": 357222.0,
      "text": "Quick aside: palliative care -- a very important field but poorly understood --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 357222.0,
      "end_time": 360200.0,
      "text": "while it includes, it is not limited to end of life care."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 360200.0,
      "end_time": 362811.0,
      "text": "It is not limited to hospice."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 362811.0,
      "end_time": 366999.0,
      "text": "It's simply about comfort and living well at any stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 366999.0,
      "end_time": 370062.0,
      "text": "So please know that you don't have to be dying anytime soon"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 370062.0,
      "end_time": 373450.0,
      "text": "to benefit from palliative care."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 373450.0,
      "end_time": 377768.0,
      "text": "Now, let me introduce you to Frank."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 377768.0,
      "end_time": 379007.0,
      "text": "Sort of makes this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 379007.0,
      "end_time": 381061.0,
      "text": "I've been seeing Frank now for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 381061.0,
      "end_time": 386197.0,
      "text": "He's living with advancing prostate cancer on top of long-standing HIV."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 386197.0,
      "end_time": 388207.0,
      "text": "We work on his bone pain and his fatigue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 388207.0,
      "end_time": 392945.0,
      "text": "but most of the time we spend thinking out loud together about his life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 392945.0,
      "end_time": 395071.0,
      "text": "really, about our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 395071.0,
      "end_time": 397207.0,
      "text": "In this way, Frank grieves."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 397207.0,
      "end_time": 401010.0,
      "text": "In this way, he keeps up with his losses as they roll in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 401010.0,
      "end_time": 405524.0,
      "text": "so that he's ready to take in the next moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 405524.0,
      "end_time": 411243.0,
      "text": "Loss is one thing, but regret, quite another."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 411243.0,
      "end_time": 413224.0,
      "text": "Frank has always been an adventurer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 413224.0,
      "end_time": 416089.0,
      "text": "he looks like something out of a Norman Rockwell painting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 416089.0,
      "end_time": 418566.0,
      "text": "and no fan of regret."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 418566.0,
      "end_time": 421271.0,
      "text": "So it wasn't surprising when he came into clinic one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 421271.0,
      "end_time": 425142.0,
      "text": "saying he wanted to raft down the Colorado River."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 425142.0,
      "end_time": 427268.0,
      "text": "Was this a good idea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 427268.0,
      "end_time": 431496.0,
      "text": "With all the risks to his safety and his health, some would say no."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 431496.0,
      "end_time": 435999.0,
      "text": "Many did, but he went for it, while he still could."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 435999.0,
      "end_time": 440928.0,
      "text": "It was a glorious, marvelous trip:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 440928.0,
      "end_time": 446274.0,
      "text": "freezing water, blistering dry heat, scorpions, snakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 446274.0,
      "end_time": 451729.0,
      "text": "wildlife howling off the flaming walls of the Grand Canyon --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 451729.0,
      "end_time": 456492.0,
      "text": "all the glorious side of the world beyond our control."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 456492.0,
      "end_time": 458406.0,
      "text": "Frank's decision, while maybe dramatic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 458406.0,
      "end_time": 460717.0,
      "text": "is exactly the kind so many of us would make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 460717.0,
      "end_time": 469291.0,
      "text": "if we only had the support to figure out what is best for ourselves over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 469291.0,
      "end_time": 474723.0,
      "text": "So much of what we're talking about today is a shift in perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 474723.0,
      "end_time": 476999.0,
      "text": "After my accident, when I went back to college,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 476999.0,
      "end_time": 480095.0,
      "text": "I changed my major to art history."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 480095.0,
      "end_time": 485705.0,
      "text": "Studying visual art, I figured I'd learn something about how to see --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 485705.0,
      "end_time": 489103.0,
      "text": "a really potent lesson for a kid who couldn't change"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 489103.0,
      "end_time": 492602.0,
      "text": "so much of what he was seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 492602.0,
      "end_time": 496364.0,
      "text": "Perspective, that kind of alchemy we humans get to play with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 496364.0,
      "end_time": 501999.0,
      "text": "turning anguish into a flower."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 501999.0,
      "end_time": 505815.0,
      "text": "Flash forward: now I work at an amazing place in San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 505815.0,
      "end_time": 508078.0,
      "text": "called the Zen Hospice Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 508078.0,
      "end_time": 512405.0,
      "text": "where we have a little ritual that helps with this shift in perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 512405.0,
      "end_time": 515490.0,
      "text": "When one of our residents dies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 515490.0,
      "end_time": 519984.0,
      "text": "the mortuary men come, and as we're wheeling the body out through the garden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 519984.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522038.00000000006,
      "text": "heading for the gate, we pause."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 522038.0,
      "end_time": 524247.0,
      "text": "Anyone who wants --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 524246.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526995.0,
      "text": "fellow residents, family, nurses, volunteers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 526995.0,
      "end_time": 529463.0,
      "text": "the hearse drivers too, now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 529463.0,
      "end_time": 533914.0,
      "text": "shares a story or a song or silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 533914.0,
      "end_time": 537282.0,
      "text": "as we sprinkle the body with flower petals."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 537282.0,
      "end_time": 539610.0,
      "text": "It takes a few minutes;"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 539610.0,
      "end_time": 544999.0,
      "text": "it's a sweet, simple parting image to usher in grief with warmth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 544999.0,
      "end_time": 548060.0,
      "text": "rather than repugnance."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 548060.0,
      "end_time": 553130.0,
      "text": "Contrast that with the typical experience in the hospital setting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 553130.0,
      "end_time": 558018.0,
      "text": "much like this -- floodlit room lined with tubes and beeping machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 558018.0,
      "end_time": 563419.0,
      "text": "and blinking lights that don't stop even when the patient's life has."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 563419.0,
      "end_time": 566469.0,
      "text": "Cleaning crew swoops in, the body's whisked away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 566469.0,
      "end_time": 573070.0,
      "text": "and it all feels as though that person had never really existed."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 573070.0,
      "end_time": 575717.0,
      "text": "Well-intended, of course, in the name of sterility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 575717.0,
      "end_time": 579237.0,
      "text": "but hospitals tend to assault our senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 579237.0,
      "end_time": 584765.0,
      "text": "and the most we might hope for within those walls is numbness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 584765.0,
      "end_time": 590499.0,
      "text": "anesthetic, literally the opposite of aesthetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 590499.0,
      "end_time": 596096.0,
      "text": "I revere hospitals for what they can do; I am alive because of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 596096.0,
      "end_time": 599436.0,
      "text": "But we ask too much of our hospitals."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 599436.0,
      "end_time": 603053.0,
      "text": "They are places for acute trauma and treatable illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 603053.0,
      "end_time": 610078.0,
      "text": "They are no place to live and die; that's not what they were designed for."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 610078.0,
      "end_time": 612402.0,
      "text": "Now mind you -- I am not giving up on the notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 612402.0,
      "end_time": 616057.0,
      "text": "that our institutions can become more humane."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 616057.0,
      "end_time": 621092.0,
      "text": "Beauty can be found anywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 621092.0,
      "end_time": 623388.0,
      "text": "I spent a few months in a burn unit"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 623388.0,
      "end_time": 626160.0,
      "text": "at St. Barnabas Hospital in Livingston, New Jersey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 626160.0,
      "end_time": 630341.0,
      "text": "where I got really great care at every turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 630341.0,
      "end_time": 633415.0,
      "text": "including good palliative care for my pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 633415.0,
      "end_time": 637426.0,
      "text": "And one night, it began to snow outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 637426.0,
      "end_time": 642103.0,
      "text": "I remember my nurses complaining about driving through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 642103.0,
      "end_time": 644311.0,
      "text": "And there was no window in my room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 644311.0,
      "end_time": 649299.0,
      "text": "but it was great to just imagine it coming down all sticky."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 649299.0,
      "end_time": 653257.0,
      "text": "Next day, one of my nurses smuggled in a snowball for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 653257.0,
      "end_time": 656731.0,
      "text": "She brought it in to the unit."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 656731.0,
      "end_time": 662163.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you the rapture I felt holding that in my hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 662163.0,
      "end_time": 665236.0,
      "text": "and the coldness dripping onto my burning skin;"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 665236.0,
      "end_time": 667570.0,
      "text": "the miracle of it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 667570.0,
      "end_time": 675293.0,
      "text": "the fascination as I watched it melt and turn into water."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 675293.0,
      "end_time": 677448.0,
      "text": "In that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 677448.0,
      "end_time": 681960.0,
      "text": "just being any part of this planet in this universe mattered more to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 681960.0,
      "end_time": 684083.0,
      "text": "than whether I lived or died."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 684083.0,
      "end_time": 687230.0,
      "text": "That little snowball packed all the inspiration I needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 687230.0,
      "end_time": 691176.0,
      "text": "to both try to live and be OK if I did not."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 691176.0,
      "end_time": 696356.0,
      "text": "In a hospital, that's a stolen moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 696356.0,
      "end_time": 699769.0,
      "text": "In my work over the years, I've known many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 699769.0,
      "end_time": 703192.0,
      "text": "who were ready to go, ready to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 703192.0,
      "end_time": 707999.0,
      "text": "Not because they had found some final peace or transcendence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 707999.0,
      "end_time": 714553.0,
      "text": "but because they were so repulsed by what their lives had become --"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 714553.0,
      "end_time": 723394.0,
      "text": "in a word, cut off, or ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 723394.0,
      "end_time": 729504.0,
      "text": "There are already record numbers of us living with chronic and terminal illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 729504.0,
      "end_time": 731947.0,
      "text": "and into ever older age."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 731947.0,
      "end_time": 739335.0,
      "text": "And we are nowhere near ready or prepared for this silver tsunami."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 739335.0,
      "end_time": 742620.0,
      "text": "We need an infrastructure dynamic enough to handle"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 742620.0,
      "end_time": 747637.0,
      "text": "these seismic shifts in our population."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 747637.0,
      "end_time": 750681.0,
      "text": "Now is the time to create something new, something vital."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 750681.0,
      "end_time": 753065.0,
      "text": "I know we can because we have to."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 753065.0,
      "end_time": 755651.0,
      "text": "The alternative is just unacceptable."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 755651.0,
      "end_time": 757557.0,
      "text": "And the key ingredients are known:"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 757557.0,
      "end_time": 761255.0,
      "text": "policy, education and training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 761255.0,
      "end_time": 764642.0,
      "text": "systems, bricks and mortar."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 764642.0,
      "end_time": 769123.0,
      "text": "We have tons of input for designers of all stripes to work with."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 769123.0,
      "end_time": 771028.0,
      "text": "We know, for example, from research"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 771028.0,
      "end_time": 774538.0,
      "text": "what's most important to people who are closer to death:"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 774538.0,
      "end_time": 781527.0,
      "text": "comfort; feeling unburdened and unburdening to those they love;"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 781527.0,
      "end_time": 788896.0,
      "text": "existential peace; and a sense of wonderment and spirituality."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 788896.0,
      "end_time": 792678.0,
      "text": "Over Zen Hospice's nearly 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 792678.0,
      "end_time": 797662.0,
      "text": "we've learned much more from our residents in subtle detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 797662.0,
      "end_time": 801499.0,
      "text": "Little things aren't so little."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 801499.0,
      "end_time": 802697.0,
      "text": "Take Janette."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 802697.0,
      "end_time": 806208.0,
      "text": "She finds it harder to breathe one day to the next due to ALS."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 806208.0,
      "end_time": 808121.0,
      "text": "Well, guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 808121.0,
      "end_time": 811523.0,
      "text": "She wants to start smoking again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 811523.0,
      "end_time": 816786.0,
      "text": "and French cigarettes, if you please."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 816786.0,
      "end_time": 819033.0,
      "text": "Not out of some self-destructive bent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 819033.0,
      "end_time": 824786.0,
      "text": "but to feel her lungs filled while she has them."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 824786.0,
      "end_time": 827556.0,
      "text": "Priorities change."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 827556.0,
      "end_time": 830051.0,
      "text": "Or Kate -- she just wants to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 830051.0,
      "end_time": 834110.0,
      "text": "her dog Austin is lying at the foot of her bed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 834110.0,
      "end_time": 837851.0,
      "text": "his cold muzzle against her dry skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 837851.0,
      "end_time": 840598.0,
      "text": "instead of more chemotherapy coursing through her veins --"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 840598.0,
      "end_time": 842849.0,
      "text": "she's done that."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 842849.0,
      "end_time": 847889.0,
      "text": "Sensuous, aesthetic gratification, where in a moment, in an instant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 847889.0,
      "end_time": 855373.0,
      "text": "we are rewarded for just being."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 855373.0,
      "end_time": 859679.0,
      "text": "So much of it comes down to loving our time by way of the senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 859679.0,
      "end_time": 866258.0,
      "text": "by way of the body -- the very thing doing the living and the dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 866258.0,
      "end_time": 867841.0,
      "text": "Probably the most poignant room"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 867841.0,
      "end_time": 870118.0,
      "text": "in the Zen Hospice guest house is our kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 870118.0,
      "end_time": 872179.0,
      "text": "which is a little strange when you realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 872179.0,
      "end_time": 876016.0,
      "text": "that so many of our residents can eat very little, if anything at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 876016.0,
      "end_time": 881910.0,
      "text": "But we realize we are providing sustenance on several levels:"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 881910.0,
      "end_time": 886356.0,
      "text": "smell, a symbolic plane."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 886356.0,
      "end_time": 891297.0,
      "text": "Seriously, with all the heavy-duty stuff happening under our roof,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 891297.0,
      "end_time": 895055.0,
      "text": "one of the most tried and true interventions we know of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 895055.0,
      "end_time": 910144.0,
      "text": "is to bake cookies."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 910144.0,
      "end_time": 911772.0,
      "text": "As long as we have our senses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 911772.0,
      "end_time": 913808.0,
      "text": "even just one --"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 913808.0,
      "end_time": 917241.0,
      "text": "we have at least the possibility of accessing"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 917241.0,
      "end_time": 922999.0,
      "text": "what makes us feel human, connected."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 922999.0,
      "end_time": 925809.0,
      "text": "Imagine the ripples of this notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 925809.0,
      "end_time": 929554.0,
      "text": "for the millions of people living and dying with dementia."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 929554.0,
      "end_time": 933843.0,
      "text": "Primal sensorial delights that say the things we don't have words for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 933843.0,
      "end_time": 936741.0,
      "text": "impulses that make us stay present --"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 936741.0,
      "end_time": 942280.0,
      "text": "no need for a past or a future."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 942280.0,
      "end_time": 950559.0,
      "text": "So, if teasing unnecessary suffering out of the system was our first design cue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 950559.0,
      "end_time": 953287.0,
      "text": "then tending to dignity by way of the senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 953287.0,
      "end_time": 957103.0,
      "text": "by way of the body -- the aesthetic realm --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 957103.0,
      "end_time": 959944.0,
      "text": "is design cue number two."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 959944.0,
      "end_time": 963774.0,
      "text": "Now this gets us quickly to the third and final bit for today;"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 963774.0,
      "end_time": 970662.0,
      "text": "namely, we need to lift our sights, to set our sights on well-being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 970662.0,
      "end_time": 973999.0,
      "text": "so that life and health and healthcare"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 973999.0,
      "end_time": 976408.0,
      "text": "can become about making life more wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 976408.0,
      "end_time": 980196.0,
      "text": "rather than just less horrible."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 980196.0,
      "end_time": 982999.0,
      "text": "Beneficence."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 982999.0,
      "end_time": 985158.0,
      "text": "Here, this gets right at the distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 985158.0,
      "end_time": 990316.0,
      "text": "between a disease-centered and a patient- or human-centered model of care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 990316.0,
      "end_time": 993801.0,
      "text": "and here is where caring becomes a creative, generative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 993801.0,
      "end_time": 996657.0,
      "text": "even playful act."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 996657.0,
      "end_time": 999687.0,
      "text": "\"Play\" may sound like a funny word here."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 999687.0,
      "end_time": 1002615.0,
      "text": "But it is also one of our highest forms of adaptation."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 1002610.0,
      "end_time": 1007293.0,
      "text": "Consider every major compulsory effort it takes to be human."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 1007300.0,
      "end_time": 1009827.0,
      "text": "The need for food has birthed cuisine."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1009830.0,
      "end_time": 1012442.0,
      "text": "The need for shelter has given rise to architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 1012440.0,
      "end_time": 1014670.0,
      "text": "The need for cover, fashion."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 1014670.0,
      "end_time": 1017425.0,
      "text": "And for being subjected to the clock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 1017420.0,
      "end_time": 1023764.0,
      "text": "well, we invented music."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 1023770.0,
      "end_time": 1027003.0,
      "text": "So, since dying is a necessary part of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 1027000.0,
      "end_time": 1032055.0,
      "text": "what might we create with this fact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 1032050.0,
      "end_time": 1035450.0,
      "text": "By \"play\" I am in no way suggesting we take a light approach to dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1035450.0,
      "end_time": 1038113.0,
      "text": "or that we mandate any particular way of dying."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1038119.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1041001.9999999999,
      "text": "There are mountains of sorrow that cannot move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1041000.0,
      "end_time": 1045000.0,
      "text": "and one way or another, we will all kneel there."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1045000.0,
      "end_time": 1048525.0,
      "text": "Rather, I am asking that we make space --"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1048520.0,
      "end_time": 1054287.0,
      "text": "physical, psychic room, to allow life to play itself all the way out --"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1054290.0,
      "end_time": 1057671.0,
      "text": "so that rather than just getting out of the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1057670.0,
      "end_time": 1064929.0,
      "text": "aging and dying can become a process of crescendo through to the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1064930.0,
      "end_time": 1070282.0,
      "text": "We can't solve for death."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1070280.0,
      "end_time": 1072611.0,
      "text": "I know some of you are working on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1072610.0,
      "end_time": 1076999.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1077000.0,
      "end_time": 1078836.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, we can --"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1078840.0,
      "end_time": 1080880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1080880.0,
      "end_time": 1084043.0,
      "text": "We can design towards it."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1084040.0,
      "end_time": 1085439.0,
      "text": "Parts of me died early on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1085440.0,
      "end_time": 1088582.0,
      "text": "and that's something we can all say one way or another."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1088580.0,
      "end_time": 1091245.0,
      "text": "I got to redesign my life around this fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1091250.0,
      "end_time": 1094614.0,
      "text": "and I tell you it has been a liberation"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1094610.0,
      "end_time": 1097789.0,
      "text": "to realize you can always find a shock of beauty or meaning"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1097790.0,
      "end_time": 1100081.0,
      "text": "in what life you have left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1100080.0,
      "end_time": 1102868.0,
      "text": "like that snowball lasting for a perfect moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1102870.0,
      "end_time": 1106700.0,
      "text": "all the while melting away."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1106700.0,
      "end_time": 1112743.0,
      "text": "If we love such moments ferociously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1112740.0,
      "end_time": 1115036.0,
      "text": "then maybe we can learn to live well --"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1115040.0,
      "end_time": 1117151.0,
      "text": "not in spite of death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1117150.0,
      "end_time": 1122520.0,
      "text": "but because of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1122520.0,
      "end_time": 1124720.0,
      "text": "Let death be what takes us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1124720.0,
      "end_time": 1128868.0,
      "text": "not lack of imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1128870.0,
      "end_time": 1130046.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1130040.0,
      "end_time": 1140040.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}